    Massive change of zend_error() to php_error().

    * ext/standard/basic_functions.c
      ext/standard/basic_functions.h:
    * Makefile.am: Add mergesort.c to compilation list.

    * mergesort.c
      php.h: Added mergesort.c from FreeBSD.

